[30;1m165 | [0m[35m          `max(1, int(max_features * n_features_in_))` features are considered at each[0m
[30;1m166 | [0m[35m          split.[0m
[30;1m167 | [0m[35m        - If "sqrt", then `max_features=sqrt(n_features)`.[0m
[30;1m168 | [0m[35m        - If "log2", then `max_features=log2(n_features)`.[0m
